snippet.title: Mercury Hg - Debut Trailer (PS3, Xbox 360)
snippet.description:
Watch as the star of the game, the Mercury blob, makes its way through a myriad of moving levels based on the periodic table of elements.

Read more here: http://www.gamespot.com/632842
